objects.definition: A quality assessment has been made and enough of the data quality objectives have not been met that the observation has been assessed to be of bad quality.
objects.name: Bad

objects.definition: A quality assessment has been made and all data quality objectives have been met.
objects.name: Good

objects.definition: A quality assessment has been made and one or more data quality objectives has not been met. The observation may be suspect and has been assessed to be of marginal quality.
objects.name: Marginal

objects.definition: No data quality assessment has been made.
objects.name: None

objects.definition: The quality of the observation is unknown.
objects.name: Unknown
